---
import { SEMINARIO, CHECKOUT_GRATUITO, CHECKOUT_VIP, CHECKOUT_PLATINUM } from '../config/seminario';
---
<section id="tiers" class="py-14 md:py-20 px-5" style="background-color: #f8f9fb;">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">

    <div class="text-center mb-10 md:mb-14">
      <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-2" style="color: #e8590c;">
        Escolha sua participação
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Garanta sua vaga</h2>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-500 max-w-md mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Cada ingresso é uma experiência diferente.<br class="hidden md:block" />
        Você escolhe o quanto quer mergulhar.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">

      {/* ── GOLD ── */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-200 flex flex-col shadow-sm hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
        <span class="inline-block self-start text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 bg-amber-50 text-amber-800 border border-amber-200">
          GOLD
        </span>
        <p class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Professora Gold</p>
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-5">R$ 0</p>

        <hr class="border-gray-100 mb-5" />

        <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-2">Ideal para quem quer</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-5">
          Participar ao vivo, sair com um certificado que comprova sua dedicação e dar o primeiro passo.
        </p>

        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2.5 mb-6 flex-1">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 font-bold" style="color: #e8590c;">✦</span>
            Acesso ao seminário ao vivo
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 font-bold" style="color: #e8590c;">✦</span>
            Certificado digital gratuito ({SEMINARIO.cargaGratuita})
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 font-bold" style="color: #e8590c;">✦</span>
            Grupo fechado no WhatsApp para receber notificações
          </li>
        </ul>

        <a
          href={CHECKOUT_GRATUITO}
          class="block w-full text-center text-white font-bold text-base uppercase tracking-wide py-4 rounded-xl transition-all shadow-md hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 active:translate-y-0"
          style="background-color: #fd7200;"
          onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#e56500'"
          onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#fd7200'"
        >
          Quero a vaga Gold →
        </a>
      </div>

      {/* ── VIP ── */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 flex flex-col shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-200 relative border-2 border-gray-800">
        <div class="absolute -top-3.5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-white text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider px-4 py-1 rounded-full whitespace-nowrap" style="background-color: #16a34a;">
          ⭐ Mais escolhido
        </div>
        <span class="inline-block self-start text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 text-white" style="background-color: #16a34a;">
          VIP
        </span>
        <p class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Professora VIP</p>
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-5">R$ 19,70</p>

        <hr class="border-gray-100 mb-5" />

        <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-2">Ideal para quem quer</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-5">
          Ir além do seminário, ter suporte real para aplicar o conteúdo e se sentir parte de algo maior.
        </p>

        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2.5 mb-6 flex-1">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 font-bold" style="color: #e8590c;">✦</span>
            Tudo do plano Gold
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 font-bold" style="color: #e8590c;">✦</span>
            <strong>Sala VIP</strong> — 1 dia antes da imersão, encontro exclusivo no Zoom
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 font-bold" style="color: #e8590c;">✦</span>
            Certificado assinado no Gov.br ({SEMINARIO.cargaVip}) em PDF
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 font-bold" style="color: #e8590c;">✦</span>
            Acesso à Gravação da Aula
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 font-bold" style="color: #e8590c;">✦</span>
            Material completo da aula em PDF
          </li>
        </ul>

        <a
          href={CHECKOUT_VIP}
          class="block w-full text-center text-white font-bold text-base uppercase tracking-wide py-4 rounded-xl transition-all shadow-md hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5"
          style="background-color: #16a34a;"
          onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#15803d'"
          onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#16a34a'"
        >
          Quero ser VIP →
        </a>
      </div>

      {/* ── PLATINUM ── */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-200 flex flex-col shadow-sm hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
        <span class="inline-block self-start text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 text-white" style="background-color: #374151;">
          Platinum
        </span>
        <p class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Professora Platinum</p>
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-5">R$ 49,70</p>

        <hr class="border-gray-100 mb-5" />

        <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-2">Ideal para quem quer</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-5">
          A experiência completa, ter o certificado em mãos e levar sua carreira para o próximo nível.
        </p>

        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2.5 mb-6 flex-1">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 font-bold" style="color: #e8590c;">✦</span>
            Tudo do plano VIP
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 font-bold" style="color: #e8590c;">✦</span>
            Grupo aberto no WhatsApp com suporte prioritário
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 font-bold" style="color: #e8590c;">✦</span>
            <strong>Sala VIP</strong> — 1 dia antes da imersão, encontro exclusivo no Zoom
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 font-bold" style="color: #e8590c;">✦</span>
            Certificado físico impresso enviado pelos Correios ({SEMINARIO.cargaPlatinum})
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 font-bold" style="color: #e8590c;">✦</span>
            15 Modelos Prontos de Relatórios
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 font-bold" style="color: #e8590c;">✦</span>
            Bônus: Aula extra gravada + Ebook
          </li>
        </ul>

        <a
          href={CHECKOUT_PLATINUM}
          class="block w-full text-center text-white font-bold text-base uppercase tracking-wide py-4 rounded-xl transition-all shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5"
          style="background-color: #ff7300;"
          onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#e86800'"
          onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#ff7300'"
        >
          Quero o Platinum →
        </a>
        <p class="text-center text-xs text-gray-400 mt-3">
          <strong class="text-red-500">Vagas limitadas</strong> nesta edição
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
